_:N3c109548436a483a9d503961530ddfd4 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Arabel Bailey was appointed Interim Lead Non-Executive Director at the Department for Work and Pensions (<abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr>) on 1 January 2026.</p>\n\n<p>Arabel joined <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> as a Non-Executive Director in September 2021, and was appointed as the permanent chair of the Transformation Advisory Committee there in February 2024. This committee provides expertise, insight and advice around transforming the department’s services using digital technologies.  </p>\n\n<p>Arabel brings over 30 years’ experience of technology-driven transformation, across a wide range of industries. She is an experienced business leader and has held senior executive positions driving growth in the areas of technology, digital transformation and innovation.</p>\n\n<p>Alongside her <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> role, she is also a Non-Executive Director at the University Hospitals of Bristol and Weston NHS Foundation Trust.</p>\n\n<p>Arabel has long been a champion for diversity and inclusion, and for the need to bring a better gender balance to the technology industry. She is recognised as a role model in this area and has received industry recognition for her leadership roles. She has a degree in Maths and Management Science from the University of Manchester and worked for Accenture in the UK for 29 years.</p>\n\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
